=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wedding Audio Greeting</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .banner {
            background-color: #123740;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; 
        }

        .banner h2 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #123740;
        }

        p {
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a {
            color: #006400;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #123740;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease; /* Add smooth color transition on hover */
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0c2227; /* Darker green on hover */
        }

        .message-examples {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #555555;
        }


        .signature {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .test {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            justify-content: flex-end; /* Align content to the right */
        }

        .signature p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 0;
        }

        .signature span {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .signature img {
            height: 20px;
            width: auto;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
            padding-right: 4px;
        }

        .record-button-div {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="banner">
        <h2>Voice Keepsakes</h2>
<img src="https://i.ibb.co/87kzVTK/test.png">

    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h3>Hey {{ $('Shopify').item.json.customer.first_name }} üëã,</h3>
        <p>Not long now until your speical day!  As part of the audio guest book experience, you get the opportunity to record a custom greeting that
            will play when guests pick up the phone.</p>
        <div class="record-button-div"><a href="https://voice-recorder-53502.web.app/?orderId={{ $json.encoded }}" target="_blank" class="button">Record Your Message</a></div>
        <p>If you could do this by <b>{{ $('Code').item.json.uploadDeadline }}</b>, then we can load this on your phone and get it to you in
            time for your event on the {{ $('Code').item.json.delDate }} üôÇ </p>

        <div class="message-examples">
            <p>Here are some examples if you need some help with what kind of things to say,</p>
            <ul>
                <li>"Hello, dear friends and family! Thank you for being a part of our special day. We are so grateful
                    to have you here celebrating with us. Please leave a message with your thoughts, wishes, or advice
                    for us after the beep. We can't wait to hear your voices and cherish these memories forever."</li>
                <li>"Hey there, amazing people! We're overjoyed that you're here to celebrate this magical day with us.
                    Leave us a message after the beep, and don't hold back! Share your well wishes, funny stories, or
                    any advice you have for us. We promise to cherish every word and maybe even have a laugh or two
                    along the way!"</li>
                <li>"Hello, everyone! Your presence means the world to us. We're so happy to have you here as we start
                    this incredible journey together. Share your love, your hopes, or any wisdom you'd like to pass on
                    after the beep. Your words will be a treasure for us, and we can't thank you enough for being a part
                    of our special day."</li>
                <li>"Hey, friends and family! It's us, [Couple's Names]. We're beyond excited to have you here, and we'd
                    love to hear your thoughts, stories, or any crazy advice you have for us. Don't be shy; be as
                    creative and unique as you'd like! After the beep, leave your message, and we can't wait to listen
                    and laugh together later. Thanks for being awesome!"</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Just reply to this email if you need any help or have any questions üòÑ</p>
        <div class="signature">
            <p>
                <span>Kind regards,</span>
            </p>
            <div class="test">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co/pvd4WSb/test-1.png">
                <p><span>Voice Keepsakes</span></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

